<Routines>
<Routine Name="Control_Pumps" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[========================================
Ensure pump required value not below 0 
========================================]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LT(DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd,0)MOVE(0,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[========================================
Specify Lead Start Level 
========================================]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQ(DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd,0)XIO(System_Interlocks_Active)GE(LIT001.Value,DUTY1_PUMP_START_SP)GE(DUTY_P.Max_Motor_Running,1)[MUL(DUTY1_PUMP_START_DLY_SP,1000,Lead_Start_Delay.PRE) TON(Lead_Start_Delay,?,?) ,XIC(Lead_Start_Delay.DN) MOVE(1,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[========================================
Specify Lag Start Level 
========================================]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQ(DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd,1)XIO(System_Interlocks_Active)GE(LIT001.Value,DUTY2_PUMP_START_SP)GE(DUTY_P.Max_Motor_Running,2)[MUL(DUTY2_PUMP_START_DLY_SP,1000,Lag_Start_Delay.PRE) TON(Lag_Start_Delay,?,?) ,XIC(Lag_Start_Delay.DN) MOVE(2,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[========================================
Specify Lag Stop Level 
========================================]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQ(DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd,2)LE(LIT001.Value,DUTY2_PUMP_STOP_SP)[MUL(DUTY2_PUMP_STOP_DLY_SP,1000,Lag_Stop_Delay.PRE) TON(Lag_Stop_Delay,?,?) ,XIC(Lag_Stop_Delay.DN) MOVE(1,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[========================================
Specify Lead Stop Level 
========================================]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[GE(DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd,1)LE(LIT001.Value,DUTY1_PUMP_STOP_SP)[MUL(DUTY1_PUMP_STOP_DLY_SP,1000,Lead_Stop_Delay.PRE) TON(Lead_Stop_Delay,?,?) ,XIC(Lead_Stop_Delay.DN) MOVE(0,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Toggle Float Bypass]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(Float_Bypass_PB)[ONS(ONS[0]) [XIO(Float_Bypass_IND) ONS(ONS[1]) OTL(Float_Bypass_IND) ,XIC(Float_Bypass_IND) ONS(ONS[1]) OTU(Float_Bypass_IND) ] ,OTU(Float_Bypass_PB) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Interlocks" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(OFF)[MOVE(0,DUTY_P.Qty_Rqd) ,OTE(System_Interlocks_Active) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="Plant_Main" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[OTE(FirstCycle_Plant_Control_DN);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(Control_Pumps,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(Interlocks,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
</Program>
<Program Name="Process_Analog" TestEdits="false" MainRoutineName="Process_Analog_Main" Disabled="false" UseAsFolder="false">
<Tags/>
<Routines>
<Routine Name="Process_Analog_Main" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[Routine: Process_Analog_Main

This routine is used to calculate the process analog values from the various transmitters. It will also determine 
if the calculated value is out of the adjustablelimits HIHI, HI, LO, et LOLO. 

//Initialization of first cycle]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(FirstCycle_Analog_Processing_DN)NOP();]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[JSR(T2_Process_Analog_Main,0);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[ 
THE TAG Initial_Process_Scaling IS ONLY TRIGGERED BY THE PORGRAMMER AT THE BEGINNING TO SET THE MIN AND MAX DEFAULT ENGINEERING VALUES AND UNLATCH AFTER IT WENT ONCE THROUGH THE ROUTINE
 
IT SHOULD NOT BE REQUIRED AFTER THE FIRST INITIALIZATION
 
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[OTU(Initial_Process_Scaling);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[OTE(FirstCycle_Analog_Processing_DN);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
<Routine Name="T2_Process_Analog_Main" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[LIT001
Wet Well Level
INITIAL SCALING OF TAGS ENTRY
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(Initial_Process_Scaling)MOVE(4000,LIT001.Raw_Min)MOVE(20000,LIT001.Raw_Max)MOVE(0,LIT001.Eng_Min)MOVE(5,LIT001.Eng_Max);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[LIT001
Wet Well Level (0 - 5 m)
]]>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[Process_Analog(LIT001,LIT001_Raw,ON);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
</Program>
